You can use your tracking number at www.USPS.com in the Quick Tools Tracking section. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Card Was Picked Up By The United States Postal Service
body: On April 15, 2021, the Post Office picked up mail containing your new card for Receipt Number YSC2190082996. We mailed your card to the address you gave us. The tracking number assigned is 9205590153708405441994. You can use your tracking number at www.USPS.com in the Quick Tools Tracking section. If you did not receive the card, please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request to request that we resend the card to you. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
